videos.headline: Mor Seck throws down emphatic and-1 jam
videos.description: Mor Seck dunks it home through contact for Hawai'i.

videos.headline: Buzzer-beating and-1 3 for the win! Hawai'i topples SMU in style
videos.description: Hawai'i wins the Hawaiian Airlines Diamond Head Classic in dramatic fashion as Jovon McClanahan knocks down a winning 3-pointer as the buzzer sounds.
